777
01:09:58,745 --> 01:10:03,123
I was right there, I was right on top of her,
I was face to face.

778
01:10:04,501 --> 01:10:07,705
<i>I wasn't even mad, really.</i>

779
01:10:07,838 --> 01:10:10,543
<i>She didn't look too surprised.</i>

780
01:10:10,674 --> 01:10:12,714
<i>Just a little stoned.</i>

781
01:10:14,261 --> 01:10:16,384
<i>After a few minutes,</i>

782
01:10:16,514 --> 01:10:22,469
