01:22:37,398 --> 01:22:39,521
OK.

888
01:22:39,650 --> 01:22:42,106
OK. OK.

889
01:22:42,945 --> 01:22:45,271
Go. Make your phone call.

890
01:22:46,365 --> 01:22:49,532
