891
01:23:14,102 --> 01:23:18,515
- I asked you a question.
- I didn't know her, OK?

892
01:23:18,648 --> 01:23:21,768
I just want to say,
it was horrible what those kids did.

893
01:23:21,902 --> 01:23:26,979
