933
01:27:36,120 --> 01:27:38,790
They're having an open casket
funeral for Jamie.

934
01:27:38,915 --> 01:27:42,865
- <i>(girl)</i> That's gross.
- I know. I think it's in bad taste.

935
01:27:43,002 --> 01:27:45,244
